dc_description_s: This data layer represents trails for Monroe County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Monroe_Trails_2018.gdb'. This geodatabase also includes the feature class 'Monroe_ATV_UTV_Routes_2018'. [MONROE COUNTY ASSUMES NO RESPONSIBLITY FOR INACCURACIES IN THE DATA. THE ROUTES ARE DEPICTED FROM LINES DRAWN ON PLAT BOOK PAGES AT THEIR WORST.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
